data.description: Don't overlook this remarkable 3-bedroom townhome! The open-concept main floor not only is boating in natural light but also showcases updates such as new hardwood flooring, a freshly renovated half bath, and painted kitchen cabinets. Upstairs, a spacious master bedroom awaits, complete with ample closet space. The basement boasts newer carpeting, newer furnace, a recently installed sump pump/waterproofing system, along with a dedicated area for your in-unit washer and dryer. Revel in maintenance-free living at its best, with additional perks like a new garage door opener with MyQ, expansive green space for outdoor activities, and a recent inspection with repairs already taken care of!
